{"tid":171207,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[白馬非馬]英法院裁定品客薯片非薯片","createTime":"2017-03-25T07:12:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T07:45:45.000Z","uid":392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28bd2b564d4b1d14ff7bd0302696b58b7fde4c65","tid":171207,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:12:32.000Z","msg":"英法院裁定品客薯片非薯片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白馬非馬，品客薯片（ Pringles），原來也非薯片。為免支付數以百萬計英鎊的增值稅，美國寶潔公司（ P&amp;G）辯稱，品客其實接近餅多於薯片，馬鈴薯成份不過半，形狀亦是人工製成。倫敦高等法院接納這番辯駁，前日（週五）裁定一向自稱是薯片的品客，不是薯片。<br />\n英國對大部份食品豁免徵收增值稅，薯仔製的脆身食品例外，要收17.5%增值稅。寶潔不服5月被增值稅與關稅審裁署判要繳稅，上訴到高等法院。<br />\n<br />\n糰製成　較近餅<br />\n寶潔辯稱，真正的薯片是不會加入其他粉，品客雖有薯仔成份，但其實是用糰製成，薯粉之外有玉米粉、小麥粉和米澱粉，所以接近蛋糕和餅，多於薯片。<br />\n寶潔的代表律師科達拉（ Richard Cordara）憑三寸不爛之舌，指品客的外觀和口感都和薯片不同，品客的弧狀是「自然界沒有的」，每塊一式一樣，是特別設計和製造，美觀之餘，又方便起放在筒內；一般薯片脆得來要嚼碎，品客卻是入口即溶。<br />\n法官沃倫（ Justice Warren）指，消費者將品客劃歸為薯片，但根據法律規定，需徵稅的薯仔食品要「完全或主要由馬鈴薯製成」，品客的薯仔成份只佔42%，未符合規定，所以判寶潔得直。<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》<br />\n<br />\n香港《民主大報》<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20080706/11315435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20080706%2F11315435&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7UzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=964d92a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20080706%2F11315435&h=784b2ae6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20080706/11315435</a>"},{"pid":"3f1ec62567b07286b9e57b7ed6ea8ff39049c98c","tid":171207,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:20:46.000Z","msg":"粉糰叔叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a51a622320e3aa13a0b0b2a9e3e9cc30ff921c4","tid":171207,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:20:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法官沃倫（ Justice Warren）指，消費者將品客劃歸為薯片，但根據法律規定，需徵稅的薯仔食品要「完全或主要由馬鈴薯製成」，品客的薯仔成份只佔42%，未符合規定，所以判寶潔得直。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7fff7cd6a60239de754e029511964652b73cb1","tid":171207,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:27:37.000Z","msg":"算唔算欺騙消費者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入口即溶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218a88cf1af5fc922fb4689434b66dc1b8e65e9b","tid":171207,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:30:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算唔算欺騙消費者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入口即溶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以為你係薯片先買你<br />\n依家你同我講你係餅乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09bbd565c1c99ac30719a4cf6674bf52316029d","tid":171207,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:33:02.000Z","msg":"其實白馬非馬唔可以咁類比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bceaee442892a06cd2e58cd05d188a484f343342","tid":171207,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:45:45.000Z","msg":"好，咁我告你違反商品條例，一樣俾咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}